            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1609328396883-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>peanut butter</strong>,<strong> sriracha, chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle heat? Go easy!), <strong>honey</strong>, <strong>rice vinegar</strong> and<strong> soy sauce </strong>to a bowl</p><p>Add 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>water</strong> and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>vegetable oil </strong>and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>spicy peanut sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/R2047Step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/R2047Step-5-x400.jpg",
